Package: roptuna
Type: Package
Title: Hyperparameter Optimization Using the Optuna Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Kailas",
           family = "Venkitasubramanian",
           email = "kailasv@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R implementation of the Optuna hyperparameter optimization
    framework (Akiba et al. 2019 <doi:10.1145/3292500.3330701>). Provides
    define-by-run search spaces, Tree-structured Parzen Estimator (TPE)
    sampling, trial pruning, and persistent study storage via SQLite.
    Includes adapters for tidymodels ('tune') and mlr3 ('mlr3tuning').
